Why use the forums?

2
00:00:01,890 --> 00:00:05,040
Well, the forums are a great
way to meet other students.

3
00:00:05,040 --> 00:00:09,210
And you can learn from each other by
posting or responding to questions.

4
00:00:09,210 --> 00:00:12,750
Another reason to participate in
the forums is to practice communicating

5
00:00:12,750 --> 00:00:15,580
complex ideas through online media.

6
00:00:15,580 --> 00:00:19,900
This is an extremely important skill,
since there are many professionals,

7
00:00:19,900 --> 00:00:21,770
technical and non-technical,

8
